                                    <strong>BASIC TOTAL : <i class="fa-solid fa-indian-rupee-sign fa-fw fa-1x"></i><span class="lblItemNetAmount"></span></strong>
                                    <strong>, TOTAL QTY : <span class="TotalQty"></span></strong>
